  "texts": [
    "ProteinGAN.",
    "Generative adversarial models were trained using the training sets for CuSOD and MDH.",
    "Then, for each family, sequences were generated by sampling vectors from the latent space using a truncated normal distribution.",
    "For rounds 1 and 2, 10,048 sequences were generated for each family.",
    "For round 3, 560,016 and 160,064 sequences were generated for CuSOD and MDH, respectively."
  ],
